## Documentation

Full documentation and API reference: https://c108.readthedocs.io/

## Installation

Install from PyPI:

```shell
pip install c108
```

Install the latest from GitHub `main` branch:

```shell
pip install git+https://github.com/C108-Lab/c108.git
```

<!-- 
```shell
# Core only (minimal dependencies)
